text: Ðis sint ðara X hyda landgemære æt Ollanege.
Ærest on Calewan were andlang lace into halgan broce.
Of ðere welle to dene æccre.
Of dene æcre andlang dene to þreo gemære.
Of þrim gemærum on ecgan croft.
Of ecgan crofte on ða dic.
Andlang dices on ðone feld, ðæt andlang wyrttruman on Hildes hlæw.
Of Hildes hlæwe on ðone stan.
Of ðam stane on ðone broc.
Of ðam forde andlang Use to Kekan were.
Of Kekan were andlang Use on Caluwan wer.
